{
  "stem": "5375.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it fell on the floor-- nobody, except maybe the birds, had any value of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you, nobody had not even a little chunk, nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said to myself, oh no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If I am free, I don't want to die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, people were dying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were eating sugar from the bags with their skinny stomach, with their [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were eating, and they were-- excuse me for expressing myself-- the dysentery puss was going out from his behind and not anything else.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were dying on the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Looking on that, like that, I said, oh no, not me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I started walking towards the exit of the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because the American captain, he just came, he said what he had to say, turned around, and he went.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went back to his detachment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I'm coming to the highway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The highway was about two kilometers from the woods from the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm coming to the highway, a bit lost on the highway.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was no cement, asphalt like here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was summer, spring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I see big dust.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, what the hell's going on?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the trucks-- one after the other after the other one after the other-- American army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, on the highway, you cannot walk, because the trucks are going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went on the side of the highway, in the ditch-- like they're digging ditches, the waters would run down from the highway.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I thought to myself, I'm going to take the ditch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm going to go alongside the highway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That American soldier saw Jude, the yellow Star of David-- Jude.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started throwing me cigarettes, chocolate, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this army was 90% blacks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The officers were white.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, boy-- I start eating chocolate.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
